{"tid":2002233,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"網路攻防戰：小米手機就算在無痕狀態，也會追蹤用戶習慣及瀏覽資料(含影片說明)","createTime":"2020-05-05T05:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T02:34:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e86f648363edbd89eead17ceb362f774dd48f9ea","tid":2002233,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:32:57.000Z","msg":"摘要：<br />\n安全研究人員Gabi Cirlig及Andrew Tierney的調查指出，小米追蹤了手機用戶的各種行為，並把相關數據傳送到各地的伺服器上，甚至是用戶在無痕模式中的瀏覽行為也被追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n影片說明：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=62kxZunBQyI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D62kxZunBQyI&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=75ea4958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=62kxZunBQyI</a><br />\n<br />\n其它小米手機所使用的韌體，包括Xiaomi MI 10、Xiaomi Redmi K20與Xiaomi Mi MIX 3等，發現它們都有同樣的行為，揣測這是小米的一致政策。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Play上的Mi Browser Pro與Mint Browser，這兩款源自小米的瀏覽器總計達到逾1,500萬次的下載，發現它們同樣也蒐集及傳輸了使用者的瀏覽資訊。<br />\n<br />\n影片說明：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1GdKvvG3zoY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1GdKvvG3zoY&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=ebf2aee7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1GdKvvG3zoY</a><br />\n<br />\n小米官方聲明：<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.mi.com/en/2020/05/02/live-post-evidence-and-statement-in-response-to-media-coverage-on-our-privacy-policy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.mi.com%2Fen%2F2020%2F05%2F02%2Flive-post-evidence-and-statement-in-response-to-media-coverage-on-our-privacy-policy%2F&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=5b8364d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.mi.com/en/2020/05/02/live-post-evidence-and-statement-in-response-to-media-coverage-on-our-privacy-policy/</a><br />\n<br />\n安全研究人員反駁小米說法：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/cybergibbons/status/1256275170802745345\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcybergibbons%2Fstatus%2F1256275170802745345&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=ab7eed86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcybergibbons%2Fstatus%2F1256275170802745345&h=d2ffd765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/cybergibbons/status/1256275170802745345</a><br />\n<br />\n原始資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2020/04/30/exclusive-warning-over-chinese-mobile-giant-xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use/#508908541b2a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fthomasbrewster%2F2020%2F04%2F30%2Fexclusive-warning-over-chinese-mobile-giant-xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use%2F%23508908541b2a&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=4eb7673a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2020/04/30/exclusive-warning-over-chinese-mobile-giant-xiaomi-recording-millions-of-peoples-private-web-and-phone-use/#508908541b2a</a><br />\n<br />\n引用來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/137364\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F137364&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=1a70ba08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/137364</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/netwargame/?__tn__=%2Cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fnetwargame%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252Cg&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktdmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=4e06ebdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/netwargame/?__tn__=%2Cg</a>"},{"pid":"c990373cadffeb2ad4fd6e7b8ab8619a13b410e7","tid":2002233,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T07:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx